name: Dinosaur World (my first game :P) Beta 6
description: This, is DinosaurWorld. This is my first game, so don't judge. but anyways, this was made with GDevelop 5. Stomp on Monsters to kill them. You can't kill Iguanas, which are green and small. But Iguanas don't hurt you. Pls enjoy. Update 5: removed caves, added second level
